EPC (RPC stack for Emacs Lisp) for Python
=========================================

Links:

* `Documentation <http://python-epc.readthedocs.org/>`_ (at Read the Docs)
* `Repository <https://github.com/tkf/python-epc>`_ (at GitHub)
